### 1. Get All Subscription Types (Public)
GET {{host}}/api/subscription-types
Content-Type: application/json

### 2. Subscribe to FREE Plan (ID: 1)
POST {{host}}/api/subscription/subscribe
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "subscriptionTypeId": 1,
  "description": "Subscribe to FREE plan"
}

### 3. Subscribe to BASIC Plan (ID: 2)
